<font color="#FF0000">SKIVVIES AND TOILET TISSUE</font><br>
<tt>Thu Aug 21  3:08:56 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
<br>
Olive drab shorts, You had olive drab shorts?<br><br>
As soon as the new guys showed up we took his skivvies and turned them into cleaning rags for our weapons.<br>
 <br>
Once my ex-wife send me some dye to dye my clothes green, since all we could get a hold of was white T-shirts. Turned out it was bright green dye, gooks could have seen me for miles. I asked her to send me rain gear, she send me a yellow florescent colored rain suit. Guess she figured she would get the GI benefits. <br>
She kept writing to the Red Cross to see if I was still alive on account I wouldn't write her. When I did write I would tell her about what was going on and she didn't want to read that. I finally wrote to her on a c-rat toilet tissue (the only writing paper we had) and she stopped bugging me about writing after that. <br>
Now I have a beautiful wife, five daughters been married twenty years have a nice home, two Fords in the driveway, retired from law enforcement went back to school obtained my masters degree and I am now writing about my Vietnam experience and other things of importance to me. <br>
But I still won't wear olive drab skivvies.<br>

<p><code>-- Cookbarela@iname.com  (Sparrowhawk) </code><p>


